{"tid":1468220,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"機場捉環球時報記者一事","createTime":"2019-08-13T18:07:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T18:42:46.000Z","uid":265161,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"deab764c81a7eaa1022cfcab689d401eb3d6c8e2","tid":1468220,"uid":265161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:07:36.000Z","msg":"P牌第一次出post,<br />\n希望大家可以睇完成個post先覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我明白現場手足想打佢，但係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">唔同意咁做</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我哋唔係黑警</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打完佢洩憤對嗰抗爭喺<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">冇實質幫助</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對手有幾<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無恥</span></span>大家唔係唔知，<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n特別係依家有咁多鬼同三毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n事到如今只會有利佢玩分化同帶風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n行到今時今日，希望大家<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔好因爲憤怒而影響判斷</span></span>，否則只會白費受傷被捕手足，同烈士嘅犧牲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n記住我哋對抗嘅係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">港共，甚至係中共</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">有勇有謀</span></span>先有機會贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">核彈都唔割</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求，缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9eb855be8d2d8f410a3f4a4ab239f86e5765bde","tid":1468220,"uid":255751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:07:43.000Z","msg":"［置頂］［緊急］ 民間記者會請幫手<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1466254\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1466254</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n文宣組入一入黎"},{"pid":"ed0d42dd4efc3c2a6e8664afb7f2e4b32455c792","tid":1468220,"uid":98842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:07:44.000Z","msg":"【訓撚醒未呀】港共政府 無辦法係機場清場 但 可以 連登分化粉碎呢個活動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1467822\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1467822</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4ecfe016c2a868ee3a3c34164c2db6d1e690951b","tid":1468220,"uid":94538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:07:59.000Z","msg":"814照入機場，但和理非主場，道歉+幫旅客+文宣！<br />\n<br />\n[推！！！ 道歉是必須] 話錯既係政府，洗乜撚野道歉既入<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1467612\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1467612</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e4d7f3c47ce50b9707108e2509fbc4b60282b3ba","tid":1468220,"uid":265161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:12:13.000Z","msg":"721 811<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"421323929c248b9de37eafbc45146023d8ca044d","tid":1468220,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:17:04.000Z","msg":"不割蓆已經由我地嘅優勢變成劣勢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1467851\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1467851</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"93a113cde0e33b6bceb26e773dc41319e1626f65","tid":1468220,"uid":209679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"